&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;DenseVector.NonZeroIterator ... This doesn&apos;t seem to work, exactly, as per the Iterator contract. next() doesn&apos;t advance the iterator; hasNext() does. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

